_sText:
Alright everyone I got bored one day and I did not want to work on any of my other current WIP's.  I made this map for fun just putting a lot of "X's" everywhere or pluses.  I hope you guys like it the game play is surprisingly well.  

There are no buyzones in the map.  If enough people request it Then I will make them and release an update of this map.  I hope you guys have fun on the map and please give it a try.
